precis:
SOQUIP ALBERTA INC. (PETROLEUM AND GAS REVENUE TAX ACT) REMISSION ORDER -
which provides for the remission of the net tax, interest and penalties
assessed against the aforementioned, on the condition that a grant in lieu
of taxes in an amount equal to the remission is made in respect thereof.
